WIP


@grand_coalition_saxony
title: We can form a Grand Coalition.
subtitle: <span style="color: var(--nlp-color);">**[+ nlp_name +]**</span> + <span style="color: #E3000F;">**SPD**</span> + <span style="color: var(--fvp-color);">**[+ fvp_name +]**</span> + <span style="color: #000000;">**Z**</span> ([+ grand_coalition_saxony +]%)
view-if: grand_coalition_saxony > 50
choose-if: year != 1922
unavailable-subtitle: The <span style="color: #E3000F;">**SPD**</span> doesn't want to form a coalition with us.
on-arrival: in_grand_coalition_saxony = 1; nlp_saxony = 1;
go-to: mp

WIP


