@no_majority_saxony
title: There is no clear governing majority.
view-if: grand_coalition_saxony <= 50 and bourgeois_coalition_saxony <= 50 and right_coalition_saxony <= 50 and united_left_coalition_saxony <= 50 and nlp_sl <= 50
on-arrival: nlp_saxony = 1 if was_nlp_saxony; in_nlp_majority_saxony = 1 if was_in_nlp_majority_saxony; in_united_left_coalition_saxony = 1 if was_in_united_left_coalition_saxony; in_grand_coalition_saxony = 1 if was_in_grand_coalition_saxony; in_bourgeois_coalition_saxony = 1 if was_in_bourgeois_coalition_saxony; in_right_coalition_saxony = 1 if was_in_right_coalition_saxony;

There is no path to a majority government for now. The current government will stay in power as a minority coalition.





